# Clinical Guidelines API Key - For premium guideline access
GUIDELINE_API_KEY=your_guideline_api_key_here

# NIH RePORTER API - No key required (uses public NIH API)
# Automatically provides access to:
# - NIH funded research projects
# - Clinical trial outcomes
# - Research publication data

# bioRxiv/medRxiv API - No key required (uses public preprint APIs)
# Automatically provides access to:
# - Latest medical research preprints
# - Early-stage clinical findings
# - Pre-peer-review research

# ClinicalTrials.gov API - No key required (uses public ClinicalTrials.gov API)
# Automatically provides access to:
# - Active and completed clinical trials
# - Trial outcomes and results
# - Trial protocols and eligibility criteria

# DOAJ API - No key required (uses public Directory of Open Access Journals API)
# Automatically provides access to:
# - 16,000+ open access peer-reviewed journals
# - High-quality medical research
# - DOAJ Seal certified journals

# üèõÔ∏è FDA API - No key required (uses public openFDA API)
